BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:TWiV 1339: Ebola up close with Tom Ksiazek
DTSTART:20260712T040000Z
DTEND:20260712T050000Z
DTSTAMP:20260720T070528Z
UID:ce83bfe593c5b828@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Podcast - TWiV
DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: This Week in Virology]\n\nTom Ksiazek\, a world-reno
 wned virus expert with 40 years of experience on the front lines of some o
 f the worst outbreaks the world has ever seen\, joins TWiV to discuss his 
 career\, ebolaviruses in general\, and the current outbreak of Bundibugyo 
