DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: This Week in Virology]\n\nTWiV explains research tha
 t reveals dual activity of a phage-encoded lysin that modulates infection 
 dynamics in a mycobacteriophage\, and refutes a proposed link between the 
 SARS-CoV-2 furin cleavage site and mouse-adapted MERS-coronavirus MA30. Ho
 sts:&nbsp\; Vincent Racaniello \, Kathy Spindler\, Angela Mingarelli\, and
  Jolene Ramsey Click arrow to play Download TWiV 1341 (60 MB .mp3\, 100 mi
